'aL-NQMVTh YHVH 'aL NQMVTh HVPhY'y.
HNSh'a ShPhT H'aUrTSh HShB GMVL 'yL-G'aYM.
'yD-MThY UrSh'yYM YHVH 'yD-MThY UrSh'yYM Y'yLZV.
YBY'yV YDBUrV 'yThQ YTh'aMUrV KL-Ph'yLY 'aVN.
'yMK YHVH YDK'aV VNChLThK Y'yNV.
'aLMNH VGUr YHUrGV VYThVMYM YUrTShChV.
VY'aMUrV L'a YUr'aH-YH VL'a-YBYN 'aLHY Y'yQB.
BYNV B'yUrYM B'yM VKSYLYM MThY ThShKYLV.
HNT'y 'aZN HL'a YShM'y 'aM-YTShUr 'yYN HL'a YBYT.
HYSUr GVYM HL'a YVKYCh HMLMD 'aDM D'yTh.
YHVH YD'y MChShBVTh 'aDM KY-HMH HBL.
'aShUrY HGBUr 'aShUr-ThYSUrNV YH VMThVUrThK ThLMDNV.
LHShQYT LV MYMY Ur'y 'yD YKUrH LUrSh'y ShChTh.
KY L'a-YTSh YHVH 'yMV VNChLThV L'a Y'yZB.
KY-'yD-TShDQ YShVB MShPhT V'aChUrYV KL-YShUrY-LB.
MY-YQVM LY 'yM-MUr'yYM MY-YThYTShB LY 'yM-Ph'yLY 'aVN.
LVLY YHVH 'yZUrThH LY KM'yT ShKNH DVMH NPhShY.
'aM-'aMUrThY MTH UrGLY ChSDK YHVH YS'yDNY.
